    "This includes facilitating discussions on topics such as AI's impact on job markets, privacy concerns, and the implications of AI in decision-making processes.",
    "By encouraging critical thinking around these topics, students can develop a nuanced understanding of AI, equipping them with the skills necessary to navigate an AI-driven world.",
    "The AI in the realm of education marks a transformative era that is redefining the teaching and learning methodologies fundamentally.",
    "This paper has critically examined the expansive role of AI, focusing particularly on the nuances of AI literacy, prompt engineering, and the development of critical thinking skills within the educational setting.",
